'''''The Black [[Bantha/Legends|Bantha]]''''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Propaganda/Legends|propaganda]] [[Holodrama/Legends|holofilm]] that starred a young [[Garik Loran]]. Garik later joked about this film after joining the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic's]] [[Wraith Squadron]].<ref name="WS">''[[X-Wing: Wraith Squadron]]''</ref>

